<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR" data-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="{{ shop.meta_description }}" />
  <title>{{ shop.name }}</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root, [data-theme="light"] {
      --text-xs: clamp(.75rem, .7rem + .25vw, .875rem);
      --text-sm: clamp(.875rem, .8rem + .35vw, 1rem);
      --text-base: clamp(1rem, .95rem + .25vw, 1.125rem);
      --text-lg: clamp(1.125rem, 1rem + .75vw, 1.5rem);
      --text-xl: clamp(1.5rem, 1.2rem + 1.25vw, 2.25rem);
      --text-2xl: clamp(2rem, 1.2rem + 2.5vw, 3.6rem);
      --space-1:.25rem; --space-2:.5rem; --space-3:.75rem; --space-4:1rem; --space-5:1.25rem; --space-6:1.5rem; --space-8:2rem; --space-10:2.5rem; --space-12:3rem; --space-16:4rem; --space-20:5rem; --space-24:6rem;
      --radius-sm:.5rem; --radius-md:.85rem; --radius-lg:1.1rem; --radius-xl:1.75rem; --radius-full:9999px;
      --color-bg:#f6f1ee; --color-surface:#fffaf7; --color-surface-2:#f0e7e2; --color-surface-3:#e6dbd6;
      --color-border:rgba(42,25,29,.12); --color-text:#24181b; --color-text-muted:#6f5e63; --color-text-faint:#a08f93;
      --color-primary:#74193d; --color-primary-hover:#56102d; --color-primary-soft:rgba(116,25,61,.09); --color-accent:#cfa66d; --color-success:#46692c;
      --shadow-sm:0 8px 24px rgba(31,17,20,.08); --shadow-md:0 18px 42px rgba(31,17,20,.12); --shadow-lg:0 28px 68px rgba(31,17,20,.18);
      --font-display:'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif; --font-body:'Manrope', Arial, sans-serif; --content:1200px;
    }
    [data-theme="dark"] {
      --color-bg:#120d10; --color-surface:#191216; --color-surface-2:#23191e; --color-surface-3:#2d2027;
      --color-border:rgba(255,246,247,.09); --color-text:#f8eef0; --color-text-muted:#c9b8bc; --color-text-faint:#89777d;
      --color-primary:#9a2d54; --color-primary-hover:#b53b68; --color-primary-soft:rgba(181,59,104,.14); --color-accent:#ddb783; --color-success:#7eb257;
      --shadow-sm:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.24); --shadow-md:0 18px 42px rgba(0,0,0,.34); --shadow-lg:0 28px 68px rgba(0,0,0,.46);
    }
    *,*:before,*:after{box-sizing:border-box} html{scroll-behavior:smooth} body{margin:0;min-height:100vh;font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-text);background:radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(154,45,84,.18), transparent 24%),radial-gradient(circle at left 15%, rgba(221,183,131,.08), transparent 20%),var(--color-bg)}
    a{text-decoration:none;color:inherit} img,svg{display:block;max-width:100%;height:auto} button,input{font:inherit} .container{width:min(calc(100% - 1.2rem),var(--content));margin-inline:auto}
    .sr-only{position:absolute;width:1px;height:1px;padding:0;margin:-1px;overflow:hidden;clip:rect(0,0,0,0);white-space:nowrap;border:0} .skip-link{position:absolute;left:-9999px;top:1rem;background:var(--color-primary);color:#fff;padding:.8rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--radius-sm)} .skip-link:focus{left:1rem;z-index:999}
    .announcement{border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--color-primary-soft),transparent)} .announcement .container{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;padding:.7rem 0;color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:var(--text-sm)}
    .topbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:70;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);background:rgba(18,13,16,.78)} [data-theme="light"] .topbar{background:rgba(246,241,238,.84)}
    .nav{display:grid;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;align-items:center;gap:1rem;padding:1rem 0}
    .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.9rem} .brand-mark{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:linear-gradient(145deg,var(--color-primary-soft),transparent);color:var(--color-accent)} .brand-mark svg{width:24px;height:24px}
    .brand-text strong{display:block;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.55rem;line-height:1} .brand-text span{display:block;font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .nav-links,.hero-points,.icon-row,.trust-badges,.footer-links,.product-actions,.bundle-actions,.sticky-mobile-bar{display:flex;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .nav-links{justify-content:center;color:var(--color-text-muted)} .nav-links a{padding:.5rem .75rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full)} .nav-links a:hover{background:var(--color-surface-2);color:var(--color-text)}
    .nav-actions{display:flex;gap:.65rem;align-items:center}
    .btn,.icon-btn{min-height:46px;padding:.9rem 1.15rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:transparent;color:var(--color-text);cursor:pointer;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:.55rem;transition:.22s ease}
    .btn:hover,.icon-btn:hover{background:var(--color-surface-2)} .btn-primary{background:var(--color-primary);color:#fff;border-color:transparent;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)} .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--color-primary-hover);transform:translateY(-1px)}
    .cart-btn{position:relative} .cart-count{position:absolute;top:-4px;right:-4px;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;display:grid;place-items:center;background:var(--color-primary);color:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:800;border:2px solid var(--color-bg)}
    .mobile-only{display:none}
    .section{padding:clamp(3rem,6vw,6rem) 0} .eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.45rem;padding:.45rem .85rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:var(--color-primary-soft);border:1px solid var(--color-border);color:var(--color-accent);font-size:var(--text-xs);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em}
    h1,h2,h3{font-family:var(--font-display);line-height:1.05;margin:0} h1{font-size:clamp(3.2rem,7vw,6.2rem);max-width:10ch;margin-top:1rem} h2{font-size:clamp(2.1rem,4vw,3.5rem)} h3{font-size:1.7rem} p{margin:0} .muted{color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .hero{padding-top:2rem} .quick-strip{display:flex;gap:.75rem;overflow:auto;padding-bottom:.3rem;scrollbar-width:none} .quick-strip::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none} .quick-strip a{white-space:nowrap;padding:.8rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:var(--color-surface);color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.03fr .97fr;gap:1rem;align-items:stretch;margin-top:1rem}
    .panel,.feature-card,.product-card,.trust-card,.faq-item,.quote,.policy-card,.bundle-card,.review-strip,.cart-drawer,.drawer-menu{background:var(--color-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-border);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md)}
    .hero-copy{padding:clamp(1.5rem,3.4vw,2.9rem);border-radius:var(--radius-xl)} .hero-copy p{max-width:58ch;margin:1.1rem 0 1.6rem;color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .hero-points span,.trust-badge{padding:.55rem .85rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);color:var(--color-text-muted);font-size:var(--text-sm)}
    .hero-side{display:grid;gap:1rem}
    .hero-visual{position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:420px;border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:1.4rem;display:flex;align-items:end}
    .hero-visual:before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(0,0,0,.06),rgba(0,0,0,.72)),url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515886657613-9f3515b0c78f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover;opacity:.95}
    .hero-overlay{position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:30ch;color:#fff} .hero-overlay p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.84);margin-top:.5rem}
    .review-strip{padding:1rem;border-radius:var(--radius-xl)} .review-stars{color:var(--color-accent);letter-spacing:.18em;font-size:1rem} .review-strip p{margin-top:.35rem;color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .section-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:end;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.4rem} .section-head p{max-width:60ch;color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .features-grid,.products-grid,.trust-grid,.faq-grid,.quote-grid,.policy-grid{display:grid;gap:1rem} .features-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr))} .products-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr))} .trust-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr))} .faq-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))} .quote-grid,.policy-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr))}
    .feature-card{padding:1.25rem;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);min-height:220px;position:relative;overflow:hidden} .feature-card:after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:auto -15px -25px auto;width:110px;height:110px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(221,183,131,.18),transparent 65%)} .small-label,.product-badge{font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-accent)} .feature-card p{margin-top:.7rem;color:var(--color-text-muted)}
    .product-card{overflow:hidden;border-radius:var(--radius-lg)} .product-image{aspect-ratio:4/5;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-surface-2)} .product-image img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .45s ease} .product-card:hover .product-image img{transform:scale(1.035)} .wishlist-badge{position:absolute;top:12px;right:12px;padding:.45rem .7rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full);background:rgba(18,13,16,.58);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);color:#fff;font-size:12px;backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}
    .product-info{padding:1.1rem} .product-info p{margin-top:.5rem;color:var(--color-text-muted)} .price-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:.8rem;margin-top:1rem} .price{font-weight:800;font-size:1.08rem}
    .bundle-card{padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-xl);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr .95fr;gap:1rem;align-items:center}
    .bundle-box{display:grid;gap:.7rem} .bundle-item{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;padding:.85rem 1rem;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)} .bundle-item span:last-child{color:var(--color-accent);font-weight:700}
    .trust-card,.faq-item,.quote,.policy-card{padding:1.2rem;border-radius:var(--radius-lg)} .trust-card strong,.policy-card strong{display:block;margin-bottom:.35rem;font-size:1.02rem} .trust-card p,.faq-item p,.quote p,.policy-card p{color:var(--color-text-muted)} .quote strong{display:block;color:var(--color-accent);margin-bottom:.5rem}
    .newsletter{padding:1.5rem;border-radius:var(--radius-xl);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--color-primary-soft),transparent),var(--color-surface);display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:1rem;align-items:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow-md)} .newsletter-form{display:flex;gap:.7rem;flex-wrap:wrap} .newsletter input{min-width:280px;min-height:48px;padding:0 1rem;border-radius:var(--radius-full);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:var(--color-bg);color:var(--color-text)}
    footer{padding:2rem 0 6rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border);color:var(--color-text-muted)} .footer-grid{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:flex-start} .footer-links a{padding:.4rem 0}
    .sticky-mobile-bar{display:none;position:fixed;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;z-index:80;padding:.75rem;background:rgba(18,13,16,.94);backdrop-filter:blur(18px);border-top:1px solid var(--color-border)} [data-theme="light"] .sticky-mobile-bar{background:rgba(246,241,238,.96)} .sticky-mobile-bar .btn{flex:1;min-height:56px}
    .overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.46);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:.2s ease;z-index:88} .overlay.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:auto}
    .drawer-menu,.cart-drawer{position:fixed;top:0;right:-100%;width:min(92vw,420px);height:100vh;z-index:90;padding:1rem;transition:.26s ease;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;background:var(--color-surface)} .drawer-menu.active,.cart-drawer.active{right:0}
    .drawer-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding-bottom:.75rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-border)} .drawer-nav{display:grid;gap:.6rem} .drawer-nav a{padding:1rem;border-radius:var(--radius-lg);border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:var(--color-surface-2)}
    .cart-items{display:grid;gap:.8rem;overflow:auto} .cart-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr auto;gap:.8rem;align-items:center;padding:.7rem;border:1px solid var(--color-border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);background:var(--color-surface-2)} .cart-item img{width:72px;height:88px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:.8rem} .cart-item strong{display:block} .cart-footer{margin-top:auto;display:grid;gap:.8rem;padding-top:.8rem;border-top:1px solid var(--color-border)} .cart-line{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;color:var(--color-text-muted)} .cart-line.total{color:var(--color-text);font-weight:800}
    @media (max-width:1100px){.nav{grid-template-columns:auto auto}.nav-links{display:none}.mobile-only{display:inline-flex}.hero-grid,.bundle-card,.quote-grid,.policy-grid,.faq-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.features-grid,.products-grid,.trust-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr))}}
    @media (max-width:720px){.announcement .container,.section-head,.newsletter,.footer-grid{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}.newsletter{grid-template-columns:1fr}.newsletter-form,.newsletter input,.newsletter .btn{width:100%}.features-grid,.products-grid,.trust-grid,.faq-grid,.quote-grid,.policy-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.sticky-mobile-bar{display:flex}.nav{grid-template-columns:1fr auto}.nav-actions .btn:not(.mobile-only),.nav-actions .icon-btn:not(.mobile-only){display:none}.hero-copy,.hero-visual,.review-strip{border-radius:1.2rem}.hero-visual{min-height:360px} h1{max-width:12ch} .bundle-card{padding:1.1rem}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#conteudo">Pular para o conteúdo</a>
  <div class="overlay" id="overlay"></div>

  <div class="announcement">
    <div class="container">
      <span>Envio discreto · Selos de confiança · Layout premium para dropshipping</span>
      <span>V3 com menu mobile, cart drawer e estrutura mais comercial</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#inicio" class="brand" aria-label="Velvet Noir Boutique">
        <div class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6">
            <path d="M12 3c2.4 3.2 5 5 7.5 6.4-1 6.1-3.7 9.3-7.5 11.6C8.2 18.7 5.5 15.5 4.5 9.4 7 8 9.6 6.2 12 3Z"></path>
            <path d="M9.2 11.6c1 .8 1.8 1.4 2.8 2.1 1-.7 1.9-1.3 2.8-2.4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="brand-text">
          <strong>Velvet Noir</strong>
          <span>Boutique íntima</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Principal">
        <a href="#colecoes">Coleções</a>
        <a href="#destaques">Destaques</a>
        <a href="#kits">Kits</a>
        <a href="#confianca">Confiança</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="nav-actions">
        <button class="icon-btn" data-theme-toggle aria-label="Alternar tema">◐</button>
        <button class="icon-btn mobile-only" data-open-menu aria-label="Abrir menu">☰</button>
        <button class="icon-btn cart-btn" data-open-cart aria-label="Abrir carrinho">
          👜 <span class="cart-count" data-cart-count>2</span>
        </button>
        <a class="btn" href="#colecoes">Ver coleção</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#destaques">Comprar agora</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="conteudo">
    <section class="section hero" id="inicio">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="quick-strip" aria-label="Acesso rápido">
          <a href="#colecoes">Vibradores</a>
          <a href="#colecoes">Lubrificantes</a>
          <a href="#kits">Kits para casais</a>
          <a href="#confianca">Envio discreto</a>
          <a href="#faq">Perguntas frequentes</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-grid">
          <article class="panel hero-copy">
            <span class="eyebrow">Loja premium para dropshipping</span>
            <h1>Uma home com cara de marca real, pronta para vender melhor.</h1>
            <p>Esta versão adiciona elementos típicos de e-commerce mais maduro: menu mobile, carrinho lateral visual, prova social mais visível, bloco de kits, mais sinais de confiança e CTAs pensados para navegação no celular.</p>
            <div class="product-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#destaques">Explorar best-sellers</a>
              <a class="btn" href="#confianca">Ver confiança</a>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-points" style="margin-top:1rem;">
              <span>Embalagem discreta</span>
              <span>Checkout adaptável</span>
              <span>Tom premium e elegante</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-badges" style="margin-top:1rem;">
              <span class="trust-badge">Pagamento seguro</span>
              <span class="trust-badge">Atendimento reservado</span>
              <span class="trust-badge">Políticas visíveis</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <div class="hero-side">
            <article class="panel hero-visual">
              <div class="hero-overlay">
                <span class="eyebrow">Campanha principal</span>
                <h2 style="margin:.75rem 0;">Desejo elegante, experiência discreta.</h2>
                <p>Visual editorial para posicionar seus produtos como coleção autoral e não simples catálogo revendido.</p>
              </div>
            </article>
            <article class="review-strip">
              <div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div>
              <p><strong style="color:var(--color-text);">4,9/5 em experiência percebida</strong> · Bloco pronto para avaliação média, selos ou reviews verificados na home [web:55][web:64].</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Aqui você pode adicionar as outras seções, seguindo o mesmo padrão -->
  </main>
</body>
</html>
